4) Management of supraventricular tachycardia.[A178162]
5) Management of ventricular arrythmias such as congenital long-QT and arrhythmogenic right ventricular cardiomyopathy.[A178168]
6) Management of symptomatic thyrotoxicosis in combination with [methimazole].[A178147]
7) Prophylaxis of migraine headaches.[A178171]
8) Management of alcohol withdrawal.[A178174,A178177]', '6221508010917', '', 1348, '2022-12-03', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(24734, 'Perfalgan 1 gm/100ml sol. for i.v. vial', 'بيرفالجان 1جم/100مل محلول وريد فيال', '', '40', 'Paracetamol(acetaminophen)', 'Upsa france subsidiary of bms > bristol-myers squibb', 'Vial', 'فيال', '', 'Antipyretic', '1 gm', 'this medicine is an analgesic (it relieves pain) and an antipyretic (it lowers fever). the 100 ml vial is restricted to adults adolescents and children weighing more than 33 kg. the 50 ml vial is adapted to term newborn infants infants toddlers and childr', '0129866504', '', 10646, '2022-12-08', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(23401, 'Neotone eyes 15 ml', 'نيوتون للعين 15 مل', '199', '249', '', 'Isis pharma > biotech egypt', 'Unknown', 'غير محدد', '', 'Eye contour', '15 ml', 'indications & properties specifically developed for the sensitive skin of the eye contour area neotoneï- eyes reduces effectively vascular dark circles (blue/violet aspect) and pigmented dark circles (brown/black aspect) and also reduces eye bags. thanks', '', '', 775, '2023-09-03', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(19179, 'Floxia regulator - balancing gel 40ml', 'فلوكسيا جل منظم 40 مل', '', '129', '', 'Floxia international sarl > bio-earth egypt', 'Gel', 'جل', '', 'Skin care', '40ml', 'floxia decided to focus on sebum regulation to off er a complementary product to medical treatment and a cosmetic approach to manage oily skin and its unplesant appearance. on skin surface : salycilic acid brings an exfoliating action that works to treat', '', '', 854, '2022-07-30', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(22127, 'Luprostam 8 mcg 20 caps.', 'لوبروستام 8ميكروجرام 20كبسول', '', '68', 'Lubiprostone', 'Kahira > bioxell pharma', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', '', 'Idiopathic constipation', '8 mcg', 'Lubiprostone is indicated for the treatment of adult patients with chronic idiopathic constipation, or opioid-induced constipation in patients with chronic non-cancer pain.[L4421] It is also indicated for the treatment of irritable bowel syndrome with constipation (IBS-C) in female patients ≥18 years old.[L4421]', '', '', 1004, '2022-07-31', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
